description: Be inspired and let the Outbound Prism GTX take you to new places. This versatile outdoor shoe effortlessly adapts to all your explorations, whether you’re in the city or half-way up a mountain. With breathable mesh, soft fabrics, a waterproof Gore-Tex membrane and modern silhouette, it’s ready to take off and explore. Are you?
name: Salomon Outbound Prism GTX - Mens
